snippet.title: Bad luck and stupidity of others make us laugh - Funny fail compilation
snippet.description:
Some people and animals have sometimes just bad luck and they end up in a little bit painful situations. But some people are just stupid and do things like.. well.. you will see. Funny compilation about human and animal fails & pranks! Look at all these ridiculous, hilarious and funny kids, babies, cats, dogs...What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
